@startuml
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam note {
    BackgroundColor #F7FCFF
    BorderColor #88BBDD
    FontSize 12
}

note over App
poll核心：使用struct pollfd数组，不再固定fd位图；逻辑整体和select近似
1.用户传入pollfd数组，内核遍历每个fd调用f_op->poll
2.无就绪则进程挂载全部fd等待队列、休眠
3.任一fd就绪/超时唤醒，再次全量遍历搜集就绪事件
4.回填revents到pollfd，返回就绪总数
end note

box "用户态" #LightYellow
actor App
end box
box "内核" #LightCyan
participant SYSCALL as "sys_poll"
participant POLLLOOP as "轮询逻辑"
participant FD1_WQ as "fd1等待队列"
participant FD2_WQ as "fd2等待队列"
participant SCHED as "进程调度"
end box
box "硬件设备" #Gray
participant DEV_IRQ as "设备中断"
end box

App->SYSCALL:poll(pollfd[], nfds, timeout_ms)
activate SYSCALL

SYSCALL->POLLLOOP:拷贝pollfd数组到内核缓冲区
activate POLLLOOP
POLLLOOP->POLLLOOP:遍历所有fd，逐个调用file_operations->poll()

alt 存在就绪fd
POLLLOOP->POLLLOOP:填充每个pollfd.revents就绪标记
POLLLOOP-->SYSCALL:汇总就绪数量
else 全部fd未就绪
POLLLOOP->FD1_WQ:当前进程加入fd1等待队列
POLLLOOP->FD2_WQ:当前进程加入fd2等待队列
POLLLOOP->SCHED:置TASK_INTERRUPTIBLE，schedule休眠让出CPU
deactivate POLLLOOP

' 就绪触发唤醒
DEV_IRQ-->FD1_WQ:数据就绪，驱动wake_up
FD1_WQ->SCHED:进程改为TASK_RUNNING入运行队列
SCHED-->POLLLOOP:进程被调度恢复运行
activate POLLLOOP
POLLLOOP->POLLLOOP:再次全量遍历所有fd，刷新revents
end alt

POLLLOOP-->SYSCALL:就绪计数+更新pollfd结果
SYSCALL-->App:结果拷贝回用户空间，返回就绪fd个数
deactivate SYSCALL
@enduml